summary: Hello everyone! I have made a character very simular (almost identical) to MxR's Alexstrazsa character.
descriptionHtml:
To get this preset working you will need:

Eyes of beauty
ApachiiSkyHair
ApachiiSkyHair Natural Retexture
Any body (I use UNP)
Fair Skin Complexion

Installation:
Put the .jslot file in data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets

I think thats it. Pm me if you need any help and i will try my best to help.
